<h2>Project,Project Pieces and Processes</h2><br />
Projects have a direct relationship to an opportunity, there will always be a project for a Closed Won Paid Opportunity and multiple<br />
project pieces for products that need to be implemented.  Additionally product processes get assign to the project piece based on the<br />
product name.
   <ul>
   <li>Every time a Closed Won Opportunity is marked Paid, the project and project pieces are automatically created and <br />
   the Implementation Manager is notified via email of the new Project</li>
   <li>The new Project will show in the New Projects View and Projects in Process Dashboard</li>
   <li>Implementation Manager will make assignment to the application team</li>
   <li>New Project will immediately show in the Team's view and populate to their Dashboard</li>
   <li>Project/Project Pieces stages are kept up to date and fresh by team members updating milestones</li>
   <li>Implementation Specialists, Implementation Managers, Data Integration, Creative Project Manages, Designers,<br />
   Launch Coordinators, Dealer Advocates, Trainers and Travel Coordinators all interface with Projects/Project pieces during</li> 
   the process.
   <li>A Project will not be updated to "GO Live" until all project pieces are completed</li>
      </ul>    
      
