<h2>Tickets and Solutions</h2><br />
Tickets are support issues created by our customers/third parties to request assistance with our products. Customers can reach support<br />
by phone, email and via the new Customer Portal. Roles include: Level 1, Level 2-DMS, Website Support, Hardware, Exports, Level 3-<br />
Development Support. Solutions is the VinSolutions knowledgebase that is accessible by customers and agents to assist in resolving issues.
   <ul>
   <li>Issues submitted via email/Customer Portal automatically create a ticket and assignment rules move it to the correct queues</li>
   <li>Issues via phone are logged by Level 1 Support Agents and resolved on the phone or escalated to Level 2 for assistance</li>
   <li>Team Leads monitor all queue volumes via Dashboards and adjust resources accordingly</li>
   </ul> 
      
