 <h2>Customer Portal and Ideas</h2><br />
 The Customer Portal was recently released to our customer to allow them functionality to create a support issue and have visibility <br />
 to the process of resolving the issue. Customer can request updates to their ticket and see real-time interaction with the support team.<br />
 Additionally the customer can search our extensive solution library to find answers to their questions without having to call or create a ticket.<br />
 
 Ideas allow our customers to post ideas regarding new products or enhancement to existing products and reach out to the Dealer community to<br />
 vote and promote their ideas into action. 
 
 <h2>Training Timecards</h2><br />
Training Timecards are created whenever a customer accesses our Virtual Training Center and completes a training session.<br />We<br />
recently completed an integration between Webex and Salesforce to automatically create the training timecards as the sessions are completed<br />
and freed up considerable time that was previously used for data entry to add more training sessions for our customers.
